# Prisma patterns

- Schema lives in **`prisma/schema.prisma`** at repo root. After edits: `npm run prisma:migrate` (dev) or `npm run prisma:deploy` (CI/containers).
- Use `PrismaService` (global) in Nest; do not instantiate `PrismaClient` in random services.
- Avoid raw SQL unless the user explicitly needs it; prefer typed queries and small transactions.
- Never commit secrets in `DATABASE_URL`; use `.env` / Compose env (see `.env.example`).
